			<div class="content" id="post-content-2717661">
									

<p>A simple tale in the line of the white-knuckle action of the original Indiana Jones movies.</p>
<p>Dedicated to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-vacuum" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2198340); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2198340&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504054145" alt="A Vacuum" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2198340)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-vacuum" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2198340); return false;">A Vacuum</a></span>, for whom this was a gift in the 2016 Christmas Art Exchange.</p>
<p>Special thanks to A Random Day, Greenwolf, Taffeta, Lex1nat0r, TyGently, Randomini, and everyone else who reviewed this when it was a draft.</p>
<p>Enjoy the tale.</p>
<p><em>JC</em></p>

